author: USA TODAY, Tricia L. Nadolny, Marisa Kwiatkowski, Andrea Ball, USA TODAY
title: 'The damage was done': 89 test positive for coronavirus at Texas facility
description: At least 89 people have tested positive for COVID-19 at the Denton State Supported Living Center, a home for people with developmental disabilities.
content:
Update: This article has been updated to reflect the most recent number of positive cases at the facility.
